<h2 style="font-size: 28px; color: #333;">🧩 1️⃣ COLLECTIONS – ARRAYLIST & LINKEDLIST</h2>

### 🔸 <strong>1a. ArrayList vs LinkedList</strong>
<strong>Operations performed:</strong>
- 🌿 <strong>Add Elements</strong>
- 📌 <strong>Insert at Index</strong>
- 🔁 Add Multiple Elements
- 🔍 Access / Search
- ✏️ Update
- ❌ Remove
- 🔢 List Size
- 🔄 Iterate (for / Iterator)
- 📊 Sort List
- ✂️ Sublist
- 🧹 Clear

---

### 🔸 <strong>1b. ArrayList Programs</strong>
- 🎨 Store & <strong>search for colors</strong>
- ❌ <strong>Remove</strong> by index/value
- 📊 Sort using Collections.sort()
- ✂️ Extract Sublist
- ❌ Remove nth element

---

### 🔸 <strong>1c. LinkedList Programs</strong>
- 🔄 Iterate from position using ListIterator
- 🔃 Reverse Iterate
- ➕ Insert at end
- 🧾 Show index-wise data
- 🔁 Swap elements

