<h2 style="font-size: 28px; color: #333;">💬 2️⃣ STRING OPERATIONS</h2>

### 🔸 <strong>2a. Core String Functions</strong>
- 🔤 Create & Access
- 📏 Length, charAt
- 🔁 Compare (equals, compareTo)
- 🔍 Search (contains, indexOf)
- ✏️ Modify (replace, trim, upper/lower case)
- ➕ Concatenation
- 🔗 Split
- 🛠️ StringBuilder
- ✨ Format
- 📧 Email validation

---

### 🔸 <strong>2b. StringBuffer vs StringBuilder</strong>
- ⏱️ Append "AIET" 10,000 times
- ⚡ Compare Speed
- ✅ StringBuilder is faster (single-threaded)

